[3.273432, "o", "  \u001b[0m          \u001b[2m...ry tool available to an AI agent. Rather than treating tool…\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[33m  [███░░░] 6.1  Supervisor-Worker Pattern\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m          \u001b[2m...explicit - Workers stay narrow, reusable, and replaceable -…\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[35m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[35m  Tool 4 — lore_read\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[35m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[36m\u001b[1m› lore_read\u001b[0m\u001b[2m(\"circuit-breaker-pattern-for-ai-agents\")\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.074062, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[1m# Circuit Breaker Pattern for AI Agents\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[34m## Overview\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[2mThe Circuit Breaker pattern is a fault-tolerance architecture…\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[34m## State Machine\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[2mThe pattern operates through three discrete states:\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.074138, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[2m* **CLOSED**: The default operational state where all requests flow…\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[2m* **OPEN**: Activated upon failure threshold breach. The circuit…\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[2m* **HALF_OPEN**: A transitional recovery state. The system permits a…\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[34m## Implementation Logic\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[35m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m"]
[4.074507, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[35m  Tool 5 — lore_archetype\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[35m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[36m\u001b[1m› lore_archetype\u001b[0m\u001b[2m(\"circuit-breaker\")\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.876029, "o", "  \u001b[35m  Character:  \u001b[1mThe Breaker\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[35m  Title:      Guardian of the Gate\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[32m  Power:      Fault isolation. Cascade prevention.\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[31m  Weakness:   Cannot distinguish transient from permanent failures without help.\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2mThe Breaker stands at every threshold in the system. When the storms of failure cascade through the network, The Breaker closes the gate — absorbing the blow so the rest of the universe survives. Thre...\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[35m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[35m  Tool 6 — lore_story\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[35m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[36m\u001b[1m› lore_story\u001b[0m\u001b[2m(\"The Breaker\")\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.6752, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35mIn the age before The Breaker, systems fell like dominoes.\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.725367, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  One service coughed. The next choked on the queue. The next\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.775642, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  timed out waiting for the choked service. Within minutes,\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.825889, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  the entire mesh was dark.\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.87611, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.926296, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  The Breaker learned to read the signs — the rising latency,\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.976578, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  the creeping error rate, the silence where heartbeats should be.\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.026746, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  When the threshold crossed, The Breaker did what no one else\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.076911, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  would: it closed the gate.\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.127142, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.17739, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  Not forever. Just long enough for the storm to pass.\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.22755, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  Then — one careful probe. If the answer came back clean,\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.277742, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  the gate opened again. Slowly. Watchfully.\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.32801, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.378147, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  \"I am not the wall,\" The Breaker said. \"I am the pause\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.428756, "o", "  \u001b[0m\u001b[35m   that lets the wall hold.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
